{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Ua24zyKzYxe4BDkKNvbtHM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The \"unable to contact other nodes\" message could be because:\n1. Node 0 was restarted and is still waiting for the cluster to accept it\n2. There's a TLS issue preventing communication\n\nActually, I realize the issue might be that nodes 1 and 2 still have old certs in memory, and they're using those to present to node 0. Node 0 sees the new CA cert (unchanged) and should accept them. But wait - the secret volume update! When I updated the secrets, the content in the pod's volume should also eventually update.\n\nBut there's another angle: when CockroachDB node 0 connects to nodes 1 and 2, node 0 presents its new cert (signed by same CA). \n\nSince all the certs are signed by the same CA, nodes 1 and 2 should accept node 0's new cert, and node 0 should accept their old certs too. The 503 readiness probe failure is more telling though - that usually means CockroachDB is running but can't reach quorum, which suggests the nodes aren't actually communicating properly. I should check whether the HTTP probe is using HTTPS or plain HTTP and if there's a certificate validation issue with the admin UI.\n\nActually, I'm realizing CockroachDB might be failing on cert permissions at startup. It's very strict about this - node.key needs to be 0600 or less, and node.crt needs to be 0644 or less. The secret is mounted with `defaultMode: 256`, which converts to 0400 in octal, meaning read-only for the owner. Let me verify if that's actually causing the issue.\n\nWait, though - this config was working before, so the permissions shouldn't be the problem. The \"unable to contact other nodes\" warning is pretty normal during startup, and the HTTP 503 from the readiness probe is just because the node hasn't connected yet. This might just be a timing issue that resolves itself.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":203,"cache_read_input_tokens":40627,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":203},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40b5eac9-9f12-43ef-942e-bf88778c576c","uuid":"5e92afc8-9b6c-4f42-a653-91089f84dad1","request_id":"req_011CceoBXR5ZdWWm62JzbSP3"}
